    "description": {
      "value": "<p>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-rules.R1ew21i3luHJHfV5]{UM5 Ch.6: Gear}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-rules.wbgddINY6cseqVgE]{UM5 Ch.6: Tech Level 3} @Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-rules.aMZgpx4YpHpEBjf8]{UM5 Ch.6: Tech Level 5}</p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">This five-inch rubber ball can be thrown or fired from a grenade launcher. Once it lands, it transmits audio and video input from a full 360-degree arc up to 1,000 feet to a receiving monitor. When in range, it can also roll under it own power by remote; it has a speed of 10. It has 1 hit point and an AC of 10. It functions for 1 minute per charge.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">The TL5 version contains a small antigravity unit, enabling it to hover for 1 minute per charge used. It has a fly speed of 20 and a ground speed of 10.</span></p>\n<table class=\"NormalTable\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Camera Ball </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">500 </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">1 lb. </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">10/M </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">3</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Camera Ball </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">2, 500 </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">1 lb. </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">10/M </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">5</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">&nbsp;</span></p>",
